description: This is a market on whether Caitlyn Jenner will announce she is running for CA Governor by May 31, 2021. This market will resolve to "Yes" if any official announcement stating Caitlyn Jenner is running for CA Governor is released on or before May 31, 2021, 12 PM ET and ”No" otherwise. Official announcements will be considered as any press releases, definitive statements, videos, or credible statements to the media from Caitlyn Jenner or her staff stating she is running for CA Governor. In the event of conflicting information from different media sources or ambiguity in terms of the market outcome, the market will be resolved at the sole discretion of the Markets Integrity Committee (MIC).
